title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: Along the edges of the outer fields, the artichoke plants have already been harvested, their missing heads anything but inconspicuous.  The center fields lay fallow, recently so judging by the soil that seems to have been recently smoothed down.  As if to draw attention to the location of the rather humble enterprise of a wooden tub that takes up but a small area of this empty field, a large red kite, which is attached to a white-painted sign stuck into the ground, flies overhead in the moonlit sky.
